Class Track

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--Track
public class Track
extends Object

This class represents a track (ie a song). This class describes the track's title and duration. 

     Usage Example:

     Duration firstDuration = new Duration(0, 4, 30);   // hr, min, sec
     Track firstTrack = new Track("Tooty Fruity", firstDuration);

App Development Team
